### Student Registration API Tests

## Register a New Student
POST http://localhost:5000/api/student/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vdlId": "VDL001",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "fatherName": "James Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "2008-05-15T00:00:00",
  "gender": "Male",
  "address": "123 Main Street, City, State 12345",
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
  "alternateNumber": "9876543211",
  "class": "10th",
  "idProof": "Aadhar123456789",
  "shiftType": "Morning",
  "seatNumber": 1,
  "studentStatus": "Active"
}

### Get All Students
GET http://localhost:5000/api/student

### Get Student by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/student/1

### Update Student
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/student/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "vdlId": "VDL001",
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "fatherName": "James Doe",
  "dateOfBirth": "2008-05-15T00:00:00",
  "gender": "Male",
  "address": "456 New Street, City, State 67890",
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
  "alternateNumber": "9876543211",
  "class": "10th",
  "idProof": "Aadhar123456789",
  "shiftType": "Afternoon",
  "seatNumber": 2,
  "studentStatus": "Active"
}

### Delete Student
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/student/1
